    "MissionTokens": {
        "Contractor|BountyTitleMedium": [
            "A Complicated Task",
            "A Demanding Task",
            "A Task Requiring Skill"
        ],
        "Contractor|BountyDescriptionMedium": [
            "The latest name for our list is ~mission(TargetName).\n\nThey will be traveling around ~mission(Location|Address) in a better class of ship and with a better class of escort. Approach with caution, and try to make this a clean kill.\n\nRegards,\nVaughn",
            "Good news. Received the name of our next victim.\n\nI believe you will find ~mission(TargetName) to be piloting a fairly well-armed vessel while in the company of a few skilled pilots somewhere near ~mission(Location|Address).\n\nI can't say it will be an easy assignment, but it should at least be interesting.\n\nRegards,\nVaughn",
            "Our next target, one ~mission(TargetName), might have received word that there is a price on their head. \n\nThey have upgraded their protection detail and are traveling near ~mission(Location|Address) on a better defended ship than usual.\n\nInconvenient, but not insurmountable.\n\nRegards,\nVaughn"
        ],
        "Contractor": [
            "Vaughn"
        ],
        "Danger": [
            "Apparently, there's a good chance this scav's not gonna be traveling alone either. Seems that their little multicrew ship hardly ever flies without at least one or two friends along for the trip."
        ]
    },
